column1: Table S2 OTU table with FASTA sequences and taxonomic lineages for experimental and technical replicates. Samples are labelled as treatment_time.Nx, where N is 1, 2 or 3 to denote the experimental replicate; and x is a or b to denote the technical replicate. OTU labelling corresponds to sequences deposited in NCBI Genbank under accession numbers KT168398 – KT174433.
